## Scaling goals

Keep latency and error rates stable as traffic grows for **<%= projectName %>**.

## Horizontal scaling

- Stateless app instances behind a load balancer
- Session state in Redis/DB when auth is stateful
- Queue workers scaled independently from HTTP nodes

## Vertical / data tier

<% if (database === 'postgresql') { %>
- Prefer connection pooling (PgBouncer / Prisma pool)
- Index hot query paths
- Split read replicas when read-heavy
<% } else { %>
- Configure pooling and indexes for your database
- Monitor slow queries and lock contention
<% } %>

## Common bottlenecks

| Area | Symptom | Mitigation |
|------|---------|------------|
| DB | rising p95 query time | indexes, caching, read replicas |
| API | CPU saturation | horizontal scale, profile hot paths |
| Queue | growing lag | more workers, partition keys |
| Cold start | slow deploys | keep-warm pools, smaller images |

